                            <comment id="17906123" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 16 Dec 2024 16:57:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1922537 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/3.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
